            "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
            "body": "Calling `redraw` after `nvim_echo` appears to \"fix\" (at least visually) the problem. An alternative is to do something like this:\r\n\r\n```lua\r\nif vim.api.nvim_get_mode().mode ~= 'c' then\r\n  vim.api.nvim_echo(...)\r\nend\r\n```\r\n\r\nBoth however are just workarounds.",
